txt.en: Crocus Stonybanks is trying to assemble some camp-fire materials so she can go camping with her friends.

'Hello there! Do you mind helping me with something?

'I'm going to go camping with my friends in the Bindbole Wood, and we want to be sure we have everything all set. I still need two rowan camp-fire kits, though.

'Can you bring them for me? I'll give you some coins and other useful things for them, okay?'
Crocus Stonybanks is in Overhill.\n\nCrocus has asked you to bring her two rowan camp-fire kits so she can go camping with her friends.

'Thank you for these, [placeholder]! This is just what we need!\n\n'Here are your coins and a few odds and ends, as I promised. Camping is so exciting, isn't it? I wouldn't want to do it outside of the Shire, though, that's for certain!'
Crocus Stonybanks is in Overhill.\n\nCrocus has asked you to bring her two campfire kits so she can go camping with her friends.
'I still need two camp-fire kits, [placeholder]. Weren't you going to get them for me?'
